Package org.hibernate.id.uuid

Class UuidGenerator

java.lang.Object
org.hibernate.id.uuid.UuidGenerator
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, BeforeExecutionGenerator, Generator
public class UuidGenerator extends Object implements BeforeExecutionGenerator
Generator for producing UUID values.

Uses a UuidValueGenerator and UUIDJavaType.ValueTransformer to generate the values.
